videos.description: Kahani Smith picks up Jeffery Wilson's fumble and returns it 45 yards to the house for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Texas El Paso's Smith scores TD after Wilson fumble

videos.description: Mason Fine finds Jaelon Darden for a touchdown pass to tie the game 7-7 in the first quarter.
videos.headline: North Texas' Fine throws 13-yard TD to Darden
